<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Emare Asistan – AI Destekli Müşteri Hizmetleri</title>
  <meta name="description" content="WhatsApp, Telegram ve Web üzerinden yapay zeka destekli 7/24 müşteri hizmetleri asistanı. Sipariş, randevu, kargo takibi tek panelden.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="whatsapp bot, chatbot, yapay zeka asistan, müşteri hizmetleri, ai asistan, sohbet botu, emare asistan">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Emare Asistan – AI Destekli Müşteri Hizmetleri">
  <meta property="og:description" content="İşletmeniz için 7/24 akıllı müşteri asistanı. WhatsApp, Telegram ve Web.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><defs><linearGradient id='g' x1='0' y1='0' x2='1' y2='1'><stop offset='0%25' stop-color='%230d9488'/><stop offset='100%25' stop-color='%23059669'/></linearGradient></defs><rect rx='20' width='100' height='100' fill='url(%23g)'/><text x='50' y='68' text-anchor='middle' fill='white' font-size='52' font-weight='bold' font-family='Inter,sans-serif'>EA</text></svg>">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          fontFamily: { sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'] },
          colors: {
            brand: {
              50:'#effefb',100:'#c8fff4',200:'#93fce8',300:'#5cf2d8',400:'#2ad8c2',
              500:'#10b8a6',600:'#0d9e91',700:'#0c7f76',800:'#0a655f',900:'#094f4b',950:'#032e2b'
            }
          },
          animation: {
            'float':'float 6s ease-in-out infinite',
            'float-delayed':'float 6s ease-in-out 2s infinite',
            'float-slow':'float 8s ease-in-out 1s infinite',
            'gradient':'gradient 8s ease infinite',
            'fade-up':'fadeUp 0.6s ease-out forwards',
            'slide-right':'slideRight 0.6s ease-out forwards',
            'pulse-soft':'pulseSoft 3s ease-in-out infinite',
          },
          keyframes: {
            float:{'0%,100%':{transform:'translateY(0px)'},'50%':{transform:'translateY(-20px)'}},
            gradient:{'0%,100%':{backgroundPosition:'0% 50%'},'50%':{backgroundPosition:'100% 50%'}},
            fadeUp:{'0%':{opacity:'0',transform:'translateY(30px)'},'100%':{opacity:'1',transform:'translateY(0)'}},
            slideRight:{'0%':{opacity:'0',transform:'translateX(-30px)'},'100%':{opacity:'1',transform:'translateX(0)'}},
            pulseSoft:{'0%,100%':{opacity:'1'},'50%':{opacity:'0.7'}},
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  <style>
    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2dd4bf 0%, #10b8a6 30%, #059669 70%, #047857 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #010f0d, #021c19, #062824, #0a3330, #041e1c);
      background-size: 500% 500%;
      animation: gradient 12s ease infinite;
    }
    .hero-pattern {
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 600px 500px at 75% 20%, rgba(16,184,166,0.28) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 500px 600px at 25% 75%, rgba(5,150,105,0.22) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(circle 400px at 50% 50%, rgba(45,212,191,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(circle 200px at 90% 80%, rgba(52,211,153,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    }
    .hero-pattern::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.85' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .section-pastel-mint { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0fdf8 0%, #ecfdf5 50%, #f0fdf8 100%); }
    .section-pastel-sky  { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #ecfeff 50%, #f0f9ff 100%); }
    .section-pastel-warm { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fefce8 0%, #fef9c3 30%, #fefce8 100%); }
    .section-pastel-lav  { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #faf5ff 0%, #f3e8ff 50%, #faf5ff 100%); }
    .section-pastel-rose { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff1f2 0%, #ffe4e6 50%, #fff1f2 100%); }
    .section-pastel-slate{ background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 50%, #f8fafc 100%); }
    .section-divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(16,184,166,0.2), rgba(5,150,105,0.15), transparent);
    }
    .card-glow {
      transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .card-glow:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px -8px rgba(16,184,166,0.2), 0 0 0 1px rgba(16,184,166,0.1);
    }
    @keyframes gradient {
      0%,100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0%,100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
    }
    @keyframes morph {
      0%,100% { border-radius: 42% 58% 70% 30% / 45% 45% 55% 55%; }
      33% { border-radius: 70% 30% 46% 54% / 30% 29% 71% 70%; }
      66% { border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 58% 42% 58% 42%; }
    }
    @keyframes shimmer {
      0% { background-position: -200% center; }
      100% { background-position: 200% center; }
    }
    .scroll-reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(40px);
      transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .scroll-reveal.revealed {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0a1a18; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d9e91, #059669); border-radius: 3px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #10b8a6, #059669); }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="font-sans antialiased text-gray-800 bg-[#fafcfb]">

<!-- ── NAVBAR ── -->
<nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-2xl border-b border-gray-100/80 shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] transition-all duration-500" x-data="{ open: false }">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
    <!-- Logo -->
    <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-3 no-underline">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30">
        <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">EA</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Emare <span class="gradient-text">Asistan</span></span>
    </a>
    <!-- Desktop Links -->
    <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1">
      <a href="#ozellikler" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300">Özellikler</a>
      <a href="#nasil" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300">Nasıl Çalışır</a>
      <a href="#senaryolar" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300">Senaryolar</a>
      <a href="#platformlar" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300">Platformlar</a>
      <a href="#fiyat" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300">Fiyatlar</a>
      <a href="#sss" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300">SSS</a>
    </div>
    <!-- Desktop CTA -->
    <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-3">
      <a href="/admin" class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold text-brand-700 border-2 border-brand-200 hover:border-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-50 transition-all duration-300">
        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt mr-1.5"></i> Giriş Yap
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/register" class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 via-teal-500 to-emerald-600 shadow-lg shadow-teal-500/25 hover:shadow-teal-400/40 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
        Ücretsiz Dene
      </a>
    </div>
    <!-- Mobile Hamburger -->
    <button @click="open = !open" class="lg:hidden p-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">
      <i class="fas fa-bars text-xl"></i>
    </button>
  </div>
  <!-- Mobile Menu -->
  <div x-show="open" x-transition class="lg:hidden bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl border-t border-gray-100 shadow-xl px-4 pb-4">
    <a href="#ozellikler" @click="open=false" class="block py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-600">Özellikler</a>
    <a href="#nasil" @click="open=false" class="block py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-600">Nasıl Çalışır</a>
    <a href="#senaryolar" @click="open=false" class="block py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-600">Senaryolar</a>
    <a href="#platformlar" @click="open=false" class="block py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-600">Platformlar</a>
    <a href="#fiyat" @click="open=false" class="block py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-600">Fiyatlar</a>
    <a href="#sss" @click="open=false" class="block py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-600">SSS</a>
    <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
      <a href="/admin" class="flex-1 text-center py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold text-brand-700 border-2 border-brand-200">Giriş Yap</a>
      <a href="/admin/register" class="flex-1 text-center py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 to-emerald-600">Ücretsiz Dene</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section class="hero-bg hero-pattern relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative blobs -->
  <div class="absolute top-10 left-[5%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-teal-400/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-float"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-[5%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-emerald-500/15 rounded-full blur-[140px] animate-float-delayed"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[700px] h-[700px] bg-cyan-400/8 blur-[100px]" style="animation: morph 10s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-[30%] right-[20%] w-[200px] h-[200px] bg-emerald-300/10 rounded-full blur-[80px] animate-float-slow"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center py-24 lg:py-32">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white/[0.07] border border-white/[0.12] backdrop-blur-md mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-black/10">
      <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse-soft shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(52,211,153,0.6)]"></span>
      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-100">Şu an aktif — 7/24 çalışıyor</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.05] mb-6 tracking-tight">
      Müşterilerinize<br>
      <span class="gradient-text" style="filter: brightness(1.3);">7/24 Akıllı Asistan</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-100/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      WhatsApp, Telegram ve Web sitenizde yapay zeka destekli müşteri hizmetleri. Sipariş alın, randevu yönetin, satışlarınızı artırın.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/admin/register" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 via-teal-500 to-emerald-600 shadow-xl shadow-teal-500/25 hover:shadow-teal-400/40 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 ring-1 ring-white/10">
        <i class="fas fa-rocket mr-2"></i> Ücretsiz Başla
      </a>
      <a href="#nasil" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-white/[0.08] border border-white/[0.18] hover:bg-white/[0.14] backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300">
        <i class="fas fa-play-circle mr-2"></i> Nasıl Çalışır?
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/[0.08] backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">7/24</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-teal-200/90 mt-1 font-medium">Kesintisiz Hizmet</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/[0.08] backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">&lt;3sn</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-teal-200/90 mt-1 font-medium">Yanıt Süresi</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/[0.08] backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">56+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-teal-200/90 mt-1 font-medium">Modül</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/[0.08] backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">30+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-teal-200/90 mt-1 font-medium">Sektör Desteği</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── ÖZELLİKLER ── -->
<div class="section-divider"></div>
<section id="ozellikler" class="py-24 lg:py-32 section-pastel-mint">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-50 text-brand-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">Özellikler</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">İşletmeniz İçin <span class="gradient-text">Her Şey Tek Yerde</span></h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Müşteri iletişiminden siparişe, kargo takibinden randevuya — tüm süreçleri otomatikleştirin.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI Sohbet Asistanı</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Müşteri sorularına anında, profesyonel ve kurumsal dilde yanıt. Ürün önerisi, fiyat bilgisi, kampanya duyurusu otomatik.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-box"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sipariş & Kargo</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Sohbet içinde sipariş toplama. Ad, adres, ödeme bilgisi AI tarafından alınır. Kargo takip numarası ile anlık durum sorgulama.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Randevu Yönetimi</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Müşteriler sohbet üzerinden randevu alabilir. Takvim entegrasyonu, hatırlatma ve onay mesajları otomatik gönderilir.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Akıllı Kurallar</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Araç modeli, anahtar kelime veya müşteri segmentine göre otomatik ürün/resim gönderme kuralları tanımlayın.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-headset"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Temsilci Devralma</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">AI yanıt verirken istediğiniz an sohbeti devralın. İşiniz bitince AI'a bırakın. Müşteri fark etmez.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-building"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Çoklu Firma (Multi-Tenant)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Her firma kendi hesabı, WhatsApp bağlantısı, ürün kataloğu ve AI eğitimiyle bağımsız çalışır.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-microphone"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sesli Mesaj Desteği</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Müşteri sesli mesaj gönderdiğinde otomatik metne çevrilir, AI yanıt verir ve isterseniz sesli yanıt döner.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100/80 shadow-lg shadow-gray-100/30 card-glow scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 text-2xl mb-5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:from-brand-500 group-hover:to-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-[-5deg]"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Analitik & Raporlar</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Sohbet sayıları, yanıt süreleri, müşteri memnuniyeti, sipariş dönüşümleri — tüm metrikler dashboard'da.</p>
      </div>
